{
  &quot;prompt&quot;: &quot;A short video clip showing symbolic, emotional scenes representing a missed deep connection between two people. The video opens with a woman standing alone at dusk, looking at a phone with no message. Flashbacks show moments of almost-touch: a hand reaching but pulling back, a silhouette at a bus stop turning away. In between, surreal images of clocks melting, birds flying away, and mirrors with fogged reflections. The man is shown in a different frame, writing something but never sending it. The tone is bittersweet, with golden hour light, ambient soft motion, and a slightly grainy texture like an old memory. The final frame shows both walking away in opposite directions under the same sky, unaware they’re thinking of each other.&quot;,
  &quot;size&quot;: &quot;1024x1024&quot;
}

{
  &quot;prompt&quot;: &quot;A symbolic and emotionally charged scene in a dreamy, cinematic style. A woman stands beside a man under a night sky dominated by the Lyra constellation. The woman looks at him with a longing expression, but he stares forward, unaware. There is a glowing thread connecting their hearts, fraying at the center. The ground around them is misty, with ghostly echoes of past moments—laughter, tears, a missed embrace—faintly visible like memories around them. The scene feels like a dream or memory, with soft light and a slightly grainy texture, evoking the feeling of realization too late.&quot;,
  &quot;size&quot;: &quot;1024x1024&quot;
}

{
  &quot;prompt&quot;: &quot;A symbolic painting in a dreamy, emotional style showing a woman standing alone under the night sky, the glowing thread once connecting her to the man now frayed and broken, with a faint glow still lingering at her heart. The constellation Lyra still shines above, but she now looks upward instead of at him. The man has faded into the background, half-transparent, as if becoming part of the sky. The mood is bittersweet—loss, clarity, and quiet empowerment. The atmosphere remains misty and ethereal.&quot;,
  &quot;size&quot;: &quot;1024x1536&quot;
}
